# Bank Management System

This is a simple Bank Management System project. It allows users to manage basic banking operations such as creating accounts, viewing account details, depositing and withdrawing money, and checking balances.

## Features

- Create new bank accounts
- View account details
- Deposit money
- Withdraw money
- Check balance

## Requirements

- [List your programming language here, e.g., Python 3.x / Java / C++]
- [List any dependencies or libraries if applicable]

## How to Run

1. Clone this repository:
    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/yourusername/bank-management-system.git
    ```
2. Navigate to the project directory:
    ```bash
    cd bank-management-system
    ```
3. Run the main program:
    ```bash
    # For Python
    python main.py

    # For Java
    javac Main.java
    java Main

    # For C++
    g++ main.cpp -o bank
    ./bank
    ```

## Usage

Follow the on-screen instructions to:
- Create an account
- Deposit/withdraw money
- Check account details

